sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant UI as Institutes Page
    participant LW as Livewire Component
    participant DB as Database

    User->>UI: Open institutes page
    UI->>LW: Initial request
    LW->>DB: Query institutes with linked campuses
    DB-->>LW: Institute collection
    LW-->>UI: Render table and form modal

    User->>UI: Search/filter/reset
    UI->>LW: Update filters / clear()
    LW->>DB: Re-query institutes
    DB-->>LW: Filtered institutes
    LW-->>UI: Re-render table

    User->>UI: Create/update/delete institute
    UI->>LW: save() / deleteInstitute(id)
    LW->>DB: Insert/update/delete institute and relations
    DB-->>LW: Persist result
    LW-->>UI: Success toast + refresh list
